      "title": "Suspension of vehicular traffic",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the protest being conducted in front of the Prime Minister's Office, the traffic of vehicles on Colombo Boulevard has been temporarily suspended.",
        "Protesters have blocked the gate of Prime Minister's office and are protesting for fuel."
